{"tid":1886411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無論你係 想死/唔想死 都請你入黎望兩眼","createTime":"2020-02-19T01:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T04:22:48.000Z","uid":245362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b4ba109fc4afa492cf5cbf9a0a9580c1365abb5","tid":1886411,"uid":245362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"無奈世上有好多不測 <br />\n無人知道下一秒會發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但不論你係點既人..<br />\n你留低嘅任何野 係可以幫到人 改變絕望嘅人一生!!</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請相信我<br />\n萬一遇到不幸時 你都可以拯救到不幸嘅人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我知道香港人係充滿同情心同愛心..<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拜託你地 將你地留低嘅嘢 幫助痛苦嘅人重獲新生!</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遺愛人間</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請支持器官捐贈</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb73e56e2c4dfe280f4ec616e6a331d3322c1f9","tid":1886411,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"希望佢冇事"},{"pid":"d980f38489a6bcc844313d9f4cf93b29dacc0323","tid":1886411,"uid":7102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:37:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"615db4de951693af69ea402fcae2663df94f347e","tid":1886411,"uid":245362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cb73e56e2c4dfe280f4ec616e6a331d3322c1f9","tid":1886411,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"希望佢冇事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:42:34.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebe65b0972993f26dcb47ba28b56b3ed11c243c","tid":1886411,"uid":245362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d980f38489a6bcc844313d9f4cf93b29dacc0323","tid":1886411,"uid":7102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-